{"tid":469042,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【認真學術研究】全宇宙所有力量都無法破解 1024 位元密碼","createTime":"2017-11-15T02:39:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-10T18:49:35.000Z","uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"11d1ae729f767c582af0c4869629df18067e120c","tid":469042,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T02:39:36.000Z","msg":"註 : 2^1000 = 2的1000次方<br />\n      10^100 = 10的100次方<br />\n<br />\n已知科學事實<br />\n已知宇宙直徑 : 930億光年 （10^27米）<br />\n<strong>已知物理最細單位 : 普朗克長度 </strong>（10^-35米）<br />\n<br />\n轉用普朗克長度 （已知物理最細單位）<br />\n已知宇宙直徑 : 10^62 普朗克長度<br />\n<br />\n轉用體積 （以普朗克單位表達）<br />\n<strong>已知宇宙體積 : 10 ^ 186 普朗克體積</strong><br />\n<br />\n（參考 - 人體 : 10 ^ 103 普朗克體積）<br />\n<br />\n已知宇宙年齡 : 138億年 （10^18秒）<br />\n已知最細時間單位 :  普朗克時間 （10^-44秒）（光速通過1普郎克長度）<br />\n<strong>已知宇宙年齡 : 10^62普朗克時間</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n假設宇宙最細基本粒子 ＝ 1 普朗克體積<br />\n它們撞 1 次密碼需要  1 普朗克時間<br />\n宇宙所有物質及生命，都有基本粒子組成<br />\n<br />\n全宇宙所有粒子一齊撞密碼，撞足宇宙的年齡數<br />\n<br />\n10^186基本粒子* 10^62次<br />\n＝ 10^248次<br />\n<br />\n而 1024位元密碼 ，有2^1024次方的組合<br />\n＝ 10^308個組合<br />\n<br />\n用晒全宇宙所有力量都無法以碰撞方式，破解 1024 位元密碼<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n註 － 大家聽到的 RSA 1024 ，實際只有80位元強度。目前最強密碼強度是256位元。"},{"pid":"61f286f9176834acd6f628c9ace309fe4d10ccc1","tid":469042,"uid":41887,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T03:14:21.000Z","msg":"你講既只係brute force"},{"pid":"ee3d411df2fa89a63afbb206536b66e7aee118af","tid":469042,"uid":157977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T03:16:45.000Z","msg":"好深, 樓主係讀咩科?"},{"pid":"876c667e773f4ffa7ee703ba3a85f98e589918ad","tid":469042,"uid":28563,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T03:17:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.xkcd.com/comics/security.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.xkcd.com%2Fcomics%2Fsecurity.png&h=db449ee3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"359dea5b3413388de6f29c3715803bc2b54da530","tid":469042,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T03:22:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你講既只係brute force</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n對"},{"pid":"0ff3837157906a4da90e878aba912f520180b1c8","tid":469042,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T03:26:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://imgs.xkcd.com/comics/security.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.xkcd.com%2Fcomics%2Fsecurity.png&h=db449ee3&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當然啦，用Social engineering ，phishing，詐騙，幾勁的密碼都係冇用。<br />\n<br />\n仲有，如果你用左1024位元加密，但實際密碼係Abcde12345, 咁要用密碼字典(password dictionary) 黎破都好簡單容易。"},{"pid":"4d60e18f259c2f328a61c158cf520a4fc4c28a70","tid":469042,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T03:40:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好深, 樓主係讀咩科?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nComp sci"},{"pid":"68261ffa46d63fa27fa32ea55affdd3ba6be0832","tid":469042,"uid":2771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T07:54:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好深, 樓主係讀咩科?</blockquote><br />\n人地cre all pass"},{"pid":"933a35943c0cfd683be46bebff6abfe377f74103","tid":469042,"uid":56157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T07:58:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://imgs.xkcd.com/comics/security.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.xkcd.com%2Fcomics%2Fsecurity.png&h=db449ee3&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n直接對Owner用brute force已經解決左。"},{"pid":"666817c64ab9116dff548ba24307cdbf906fc8e2","tid":469042,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T19:39:15.000Z","msg":"勁"},{"pid":"91702be3bc733296f8f0d81ce3e914d7279bd3cb","tid":469042,"uid":77180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T20:08:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://imgs.xkcd.com/comics/security.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.xkcd.com%2Fcomics%2Fsecurity.png&h=db449ee3&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n直接對Owner用brute force已經解決左。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80449c7cee5a718baeb5386285fa5fc040f94fe2","tid":469042,"uid":77180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T20:09:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://imgs.xkcd.com/comics/security.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.xkcd.com%2Fcomics%2Fsecurity.png&h=db449ee3&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當然啦，用Social engineering ，phishing，詐騙，幾勁的密碼都係冇用。<br />\n<br />\n仲有，如果你用左1024位元加密，但實際密碼係Abcde12345, 咁要用密碼字典(password dictionary) 黎破都好簡單容易。</blockquote><br />\n睇過外國hackcon有人現場示範social engineering<br />\n好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"091d3563754fd1063f427cc3e9c075ae9c40db57","tid":469042,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T20:20:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"53fd5e4ad54119ff1cc1a8bc20437a68b86c36a6","tid":469042,"uid":77180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T20:22:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好深, 樓主係讀咩科?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nComp sci</blockquote><br />\ngeek</blockquote><br />\n好撚過你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0c6f07e64f96507a2171e045617307143e176e3","tid":469042,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T20:25:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"676cc123fd970d0c9f328798266a8232b1991399","tid":469042,"uid":44073,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T20:30:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b2b897a53eb5f643a48dc758a19f3dd18de62ca3","tid":469042,"uid":18265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T23:21:04.000Z","msg":"收皮啦烏蛇"},{"pid":"92250f07f3e1a8a36e69547946a5385fc04c1503","tid":469042,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T13:30:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你講既只係brute force</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲要係整個人類已知宇宙，而唔係整個宇宙<br />\n<br />\n整個人類已知宇宙，或整個可觀測宇宙，都無法以brute force形成來破解1024位元的密碼。"},{"pid":"b380a12577a05476afa570d7ec026da3a1ff8bc9","tid":469042,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T18:49:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}